article_title: Gallery 2: North Warren Regional High School sends off Class of 2014
article_text:
BLAIRSTOWN — North Warren Regional High School conferred degrees and honors upon its Class of 2014 today.

In addition to this year's graduates, the school honored WWII Army veteran William Beegle, a class of 1943 graduate who could not attend his own ceremony due to training.

Check NJ.com tomorrow for more photos
